import pyautogui
import time

try:
    # Press Windows key to open Start menu
    pyautogui.press('win')
    time.sleep(1)

    # Type "word" to search for Microsoft Word
    pyautogui.typewrite('word', interval=0.1)
    time.sleep(1)

    # Press Enter to launch the first result
    pyautogui.press('enter')
    time.sleep(3)

    print("EXECUTION_SUCCESS")
except Exception as e:
    print(f"FAILED: {e}")
